119
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,950
being so meticulous and patient.

120
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,390
It's because I've been with you,

121
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:20,040
a thoughtful and considerate gentleman
for a long time.

122
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:21,750
Following your lead,

123
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,390
I've also learned to think ahead.

124
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:25,600
Young Master.

125
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:30,950
Young master,

126
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:33,160
I've done everything

127
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,120
you asked me to do in Yangzhou.

128
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:35,070
Where is he?

129
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:37,190
I've brought him back from Yangzhou.

130
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,480
Where is he?

131
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:39,240
In the living room.

132
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,750
Mr. Du

133
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,040
was busy with his business

134
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:43,270
and had no time to go out.

135
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:46,240
But with my clever words,

136
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,920
not only did I get Mr. Du to come here,

137
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:50,720
but also brought along
the Young Master Du,

138
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:53,040
the Third Young Mistress's brother.

139
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,630
You go to the yamen
and bring a few officials over.

140
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,190
I'll go find them later.

141
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:57,920
Yes.

142
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,870
Miss Xiaoqiao.

143
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:12,870
