159
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:53,670
But now

160
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,000
everything is ready.

161
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,600
Who's at the door?

162
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:05,870
Come in.

163
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:11,840
Hello, Grandmother.

164
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:12,600
Hello, Grandmother.

165
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,120
Tianlei.

166
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,480
You two

167
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,750
come to my room at this hour.

168
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:21,240
What's the matter?

169
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:22,030
Grandmother,

170
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,480
Bingyan and I

171
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,080
have something important
to tell you today.

172
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,120
Then sit down and talk.

173
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,120
Yes.

174
00:09:31,550 --> 00:09:32,670
Bingyan,

175
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,750
have a seat.

176
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:36,960
Thank you, Grandmother.

177
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,200
Sit down.

178
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,910
Xiangyun, you can leave first.

179
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,440
Yes.

180
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,600
Just tell me what's going on.

181
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:54,960
Grandmother,

182
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:57,150
I've shown you a young man before.

183
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,200
His name is Ji Jingtang.

184
00:09:58,390 --> 00:09:59,270
Do you remember him?

185
00:10:01,750 --> 00:10:02,390
Yes.

186
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:05,080
But I told you

187
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,960
to stay out of it at that time.

188
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:13,080
But I was worried

189
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:15,510
that cousin Ke might

190
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:18,240
have brought his bad habits from Jiangzhou

191
00:10:18,390 --> 00:10:19,870
to our Qi Residence.

192
00:10:20,750 --> 00:10:22,510
Didn't I tell you

193
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:25,390
not to guess or speculate randomly?

194
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:27,670
I'm just concerned

195
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,600
for the good of our Qi Residence.

196
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,510
I also hope that everyone
in our Qi Residence

197
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:32,390
will be safe,

198
00:10:32,670 --> 00:10:33,960
and that Grandmother will live a long life.

199
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,150
Tianlei,

200
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:42,870
I've noticed that you've been

201
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,510
quite strong and healthy lately.

202
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:46,510
Of course,

203
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:49,150
part of it is thanks to Bingyan.

204
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,670
But the biggest credit

205
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:56,080
should go to cousin Ke.

206
00:10:58,270 --> 00:11:00,270
What do you mean by that?

207
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:01,870
Cousin Ke

208
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,030
has gone through great efforts

209
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:06,480
and found a secret recipe
from a famous doctor.

210
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,910
He even managed to get 18 precious herbs

211
00:11:09,270 --> 00:11:10,150
and had Fang Xiaoqiao

212
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:12,360
send them to my room every day.

213
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:16,270
Cousin Ke really did his best

214
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:18,270
for our Qi family’s only child.

215
00:11:22,790 --> 00:11:23,790
Perhaps.

216
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,000
However,

217
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:27,910
there's something strange

218
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:29,600
about the flavour

219
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:31,720
of those precious herbs.

220
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,360
It's hard for me

221
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:35,120
to swallow each time I drink it.

222
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:36,870
But if I don't drink it,

223
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:39,510
I feel like I'm not doing justice
to cousin Ke's gesture.

224
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:41,510
So

225
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:43,670
I could only

226
00:11:44,270 --> 00:11:45,270
pour it away slowly.

227
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,720
Pour it away?

228
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:52,000
Why did you pour it away?

229
00:11:53,510 --> 00:11:54,480
Not all of it.

230
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,910
In fact, I kept a little bit of it

231
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:59,360
for a friend of mine
to drink on my behalf.

232
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:02,000
Day after day, until today.

233
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:02,750
Sure enough.

234
00:12:03,840 --> 00:12:05,120
It's working wonders.

235
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,790
What friend?

236
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:09,870
This is it.

237
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:25,390
This is...

238
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:25,960
Grandmother,

239
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:28,150
with just a small sip
of the precious medicine,

240
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:30,030
this little mouse met its demise.

241
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:32,630
If I hadn't quietly

242
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:34,360
poured away a large pot of it every day,

243
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,910
would I have ended up

244
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,240
like this little mouse?

245
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,120
Those mice took the medicine

246
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,120
and became weak,

247
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:43,870
lethargic,

248
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,390
and eventually died.

249
00:12:46,870 --> 00:12:48,550
Isn't this similar to what happened
to my elder brother in the past?

250
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,150
His health weakened day by day,

251
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:52,000
his spirit became more and more listless,

252
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:54,200
and he died at a young age.

253
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:00,630
Grandmother,

254
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:02,840
why

255
00:13:04,510 --> 00:13:06,240
was my second brother bitten
to death by a poisonous snake

256
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:08,000
less than a year
after my elder brother's death?

257
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:09,510
Why did my original lively
and lovely sister,

258
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:10,320
Yansheng,

259
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,910
suddenly become mute overnight?

260
00:13:12,630 --> 00:13:14,790
It seems that our Qi Residence is not

261
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,960
afflicted by any bad luck from Jiangzhou,

262
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:18,720
but rather, it's the presence

263
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,000
of an evil man with a fair face.

264
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:30,440
Grandmother,

265
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:32,750
