who wants to see you.

266
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:35,630
Old friend?

267
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:37,120
The blind abbess

268
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:40,550
who died of a sudden illness
when she last visited our home.

269
00:13:42,670 --> 00:13:43,360
The abbess?

270
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,030
But

271
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,790
didn't she die that night?

272
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,600
Under the circumstances back then,

273
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:50,960
she was poisoned.

274
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:52,910
In order to find out who was behind it,

275
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,270
I used a trick to fake her death

276
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,000
and saved her as a witness.

277
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,120
I had no choice.

278
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,270
Please forgive me, Grandmother.

279
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:11,840
Come in, both of you.

280
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,840
Old Madam Qi,

281
00:14:27,150 --> 00:14:29,200
please do me justice.

282
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:31,670
My son...

