327
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,270
to get the Du family here from Yangzhou.

328
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:27,270
What should we do?

329
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,400
Even if I dress up as Li Yuhu,

330
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:30,270
