336
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:39,480
Xiaoxi?

337
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:40,160
Yes.

338
00:17:42,790 --> 00:17:43,440
Yeah!

339
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:45,160
