340
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:51,830
Your Honour, I wonder if you know about...

341
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:54,590
Go on.

342
00:17:56,550 --> 00:17:58,000
The Third Young Mistress
of the Qi Residence

343
00:17:58,110 --> 00:17:59,640
