361
00:18:39,790 --> 00:18:41,440
So

362
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:42,790
you have evidence now?

363
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,880
Yes, the evidence

364
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:46,440
will come to light today.

365
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:49,270
It will expose the imposter.

366
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:51,960
Really?

367
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:52,920
Of course.

368
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:56,830
Your Honor,

369
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:58,880
our Young Master Ke has instructed us

370
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,960
that you only need to send four men

371
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:01,830
and bring some weapons.

372
00:19:01,830 --> 00:19:02,640
Look.

373
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:09,640
What are you doing?

374
00:19:10,110 --> 00:19:11,920
