393
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:09,550
Young Master Ke,

394
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,200
during these days,

395
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:13,550
our Du Residence has been busy
with business matters.

396
00:20:13,790 --> 00:20:14,790
It can be described as

397
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,440
