405
00:20:31,460 --> 00:20:33,220
I offer my sincere apologies.

406
00:20:33,460 --> 00:20:34,610
But the good news is

407
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:36,980
that Bingyan has been treated
by a renowned doctor

408
00:20:37,180 --> 00:20:38,460
and has recovered now.

409
00:20:38,570 --> 00:20:41,570
Please rest assured,
Mr. Du and Young Master Du.

410
00:20:42,290 --> 00:20:43,220
Good!

411
00:20:44,330 --> 00:20:45,220
Young Master Ke,

412
00:20:45,740 --> 00:20:47,570
