447
00:22:19,180 --> 00:22:19,740
Xiaoxi,

448
00:22:20,420 --> 00:22:21,290
let's do it your way.

449
00:22:22,610 --> 00:22:23,260
Yuhu,

450
00:22:23,740 --> 00:22:24,660
