511
00:25:35,530 --> 00:25:37,220
Come with me.

512
00:25:37,980 --> 00:25:39,370
Here.

513
00:25:42,940 --> 00:25:43,900
Bingyan!

514
00:25:44,570 --> 00:25:45,500
Bingyan!

515
00:25:45,940 --> 00:25:46,570
Old Madam, take it easy.

516
00:25:46,570 --> 00:25:47,660
Cover yourself with the blanket. Hurry up!

517
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:51,570
Bingyan.

518
00:25:52,020 --> 00:25:52,660
Grandmother!

519
00:25:52,980 --> 00:25:53,660
