543
00:27:45,420 --> 00:27:46,810
Brother! Father!

544
00:27:47,020 --> 00:27:48,530
I miss you so much.

545
00:27:49,290 --> 00:27:50,330
I want to go back to Yangzhou.

546
00:27:50,500 --> 00:27:51,700
I want to go home.

547
00:27:52,370 --> 00:27:53,180
Don't cry.

548
00:27:53,330 --> 00:27:55,610
Father and I are here to see you.

549
00:27:56,090 --> 00:27:57,370
Good girl. Don't cry.

550
00:27:57,370 --> 00:27:58,370
Don't cry anymore.

551
00:28:01,090 --> 00:28:02,050
A notorious female thief?

552
00:28:02,370 --> 00:28:03,370
